Collier County's Only Water Park! One million gallons of water fun will thrill children, parents and grandparents alike at Collier County's premier water park. Fun always starts at Sun-N-Fun Lagoon, a key destination for all. Sun-N-Fun Lagoon includes four pools, a long lazy river, five exciting water slides, a concession stand and other typical amenities like restrooms. Join Our Mailing List!
